---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import ArticleStats from '../../../components/ArticleStats.astro';

import bottlePhoto from '../../../assets/writings/belle-de-brillet/01-belle-de-brillet-bottle.jpg';
import cocktailPhoto from '../../../assets/writings/belle-de-brillet/02-belle-dautomne-cocktail.jpg';
---

<Base title="Belle de Brillet — Vivian Cromwell" activeNav="writings">
  <div class="painting-back">
    <a href="/writings" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Writings</a>
  </div>

  <article class="article" data-pagefind-body>
    <header class="article-header">
      <h1 class="article-title">Belle de Brillet</h1>
      <div class="article-meta">
        <time datetime="2019-10-30">October 30, 2019</time>
        <span class="article-meta-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="article-reading-time">2 min read</span>
        <span class="article-meta-sep">&middot;</span>
        <a href="/writings?category=wine-spirits" class="article-category">Wine & Spirits</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p>Belle de Brillet Pear Liqueur is an original blend of Brillet Cognac and the essence of Williams Pears. The perfectly matured pears are carefully selected, picked at peak ripeness, macerated, and then blended with Brillet cognac. I was pretty blown away by how luscious it is, ripe tart, and the perfect balance between pear flavor and cognac.</p>

      <figure class="article-image">
        <Image src={bottlePhoto} alt="Belle de Brillet Pear Liqueur bottle" widths={[600, 900, 1200]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 700px" loading="eager" />
      </figure>

      <p>I am excited to work with them to kick off one of the best contests: $1,000! To enter:</p>

      <ol>
        <li>Make a cocktail with Belle de Brillet</li>
        <li>Enter your cocktail in the entry form online</li>
        <li>Share on social media</li>
        <li>Contest runs from 10/16 - 11/16</li>
      </ol>

      <p>Here is a little recipe I put together as an inspiration:</p>

      <h2>Belle d'automne</h2>

      <figure class="article-image">
        <Image src={cocktailPhoto} alt="Belle d'automne cocktail with pear garnish" widths={[600, 900, 1200]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 700px" loading="eager" />
      </figure>

      <ul>
        <li>1.5 oz pisco</li>
        <li>0.5 oz Belle de Brillet Pear Liqueur</li>
        <li>0.75 oz Nonino amaro</li>
        <li>4 dashes earl grey bitters</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Method:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Combine all ingredients in a mixer with ice</li>
        <li>Stir and strain into a rock glass with one large ice cube</li>
        <li>Garnish with pear slice, with an earl grey macaroon on the side</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Enjoy! Good luck!</p>

      <p><em>This is a sponsored post.</em></p>
    </div>

    <ArticleStats slug="belle-de-brillet" tags={["cognac", "cocktails", "brandy"]} />
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .article {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .article-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .article-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 5vw, var(--text-3xl));
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .article-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .article-meta-sep {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .article-reading-time {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .article-category {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-size: var(--text-label);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .article-category:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .article-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .article-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .article-body h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .article-body p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .article-body a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .article-body a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .article-image {
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .article-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .article-image figcaption {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }






</style>
